description:
A group of familiar faces arrive at Usakame High for a practice match. Can the Usakame tennis club beat their old rivals?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Kouhai to Harukaze Natte Shiraha no Ya
The Spring Breeze Blows Through the Feathers on White-Feathered Arrows with Kouhai
後輩と 春風鳴って 白羽の矢
